    "purpose": "Owns execution runtime state and per-request ExecutionState. ExecutionRuntime holds an Arc<ExecutionState> and sends execution update and status events through send_update_event/send_status_event helpers; send_update_event now stamps each update with a 0-based seq, and the single-update spawn path emits Update{seq:0} followed by Status(Succeed(1)) carrying the expected update count. Execution/session protocol contracts come from marix-protocol and common provides channels and shared senders.",
